{"tid":1182556,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國618購物節開賣3分鐘 蘋果銷售額過億人民幣","createTime":"2019-06-02T09:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T10:22:48.000Z","uid":28765,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5d58e607b353fa0ed80459bc5adb9a79c2c2b5","tid":1182556,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpi6V0B5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpi6V0B5.jpg&h=cefd7d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國618購物節昨天（1日）起跑，蘋果品牌的總成交額在3分鐘內就突破1億人民幣。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-02 15:30<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕昨天（1日）起跑的「618購物節」是中國著名的年中促銷活動。其中，在中國知名購物網站「天貓」上，蘋果、Nike等美國品牌的成交金額都在4分鐘內破1億人民幣（約新台幣4億6千萬元）。讓網友大酸，說好要抵制的中國人們，怎麼也跟著喊「真香」了。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國媒體《華爾街見聞》報導，得利於618購物節，天貓購物網上蘋果、Nike、Adidas、蘭蔻、萊雅等品牌，都在1小時內達到破億人民幣的成交金額。其中，蘋果更是開賣後2分45秒就達到這個目標，Nike也跟著在4分鐘內達標。<br />\n<br />\n對此，網友紛紛大酸「不是說好要一起愛國的嗎？怎麼反而創下銷售紀錄了」、「嘴巴說不要，身體倒是挺誠實的」、「華為手機呢」、「反美只是工作」、「真香」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2809871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2809871&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI5qf9GMxMWJW6noFhHuW3mc%3D&h=23d7221e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2809871&h=ce12eb5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2809871</a>"},{"pid":"42ac44a9649fcb6e04224c189df96bfa428faa96","tid":1182556,"uid":74685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:35:23.000Z","msg":"口裡說不<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcff87060b8ba4fcad7815143173e8010a1a9ae","tid":1182556,"uid":58223,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019